        (400, 'Geraldine Chaplin', '1944-07-31', ' Geraldine Leigh Chaplin is an English-American actress and writer. The daughter of Charlie Chaplin and Oona O''Neill.  Geraldine has appeared in a large number of critically acclaimed English, French, and Spanish language films. Her film debut was in "Limelight" (1952) and breakthrough in David Lean''s  "Doctor Zhivago" (1965) as Tonya.', 'Santa Monica, California, United States', 3, '/mnPoiJrhJjJArySW8wMpf84pCxu.jpg'),
