        (450, 'Mike Colter', '1976-08-26', 'Mike Colter is an American stage and screen actor, best known for his role as Big Willie Little in the movie "Million Dollar Baby" and for his portrayal of Luke Cage in the Marvel series'' "Jessica Jones", "Luke Cage", and "The Defenders". He holds an BA in Theater from the University of South Carolina, Columbia, and an MFA in Acting from Rutgers University, New Jersey.', 'Columbia, South Carolina, USA', 1, '/gAqaj4qmyhR4cCw22cmOAcvEFk6.jpg'),
