        (588, 'M. Emmet Walsh', '1935-03-22', 'Michael Emmet Walsh (born March 22, 1935) is an American actor who has appeared in over 100 film and television productions. Description above from the Wikipedia article M. Emmet Walsh , licensed under CC-BY-SA, full list of contributors on Wikipedia', 'Ogdensburg, New York, USA', 3, '/dLf79xlsmE40rog0gryjxsZJzml.jpg'),
        (589, 'Daryl Hannah', '1960-12-03', 'Daryl Hannah was born and raised in Chicago, Illinois. She attend the University of Southern California (USC) and made her film debut in the Brian De Palma film The Fury (1978). She starred in such films as Ron Howard''s Splash (1984) and ''Herbert Ross'' Steel Magnolias (1989). She won the Jury Award from the Berlin International Film Festival for Best Short in 1994 for a film titled The Last Supper (1993), which she directed, wrote, and produced.', 'Chicago, Illinois, USA', 6, '/4Wn3bsHa7Js7mYX0iehYN7BuHOi.jpg'),
