        (1066, 'Claudia Wells', '1966-07-05', 'Claudia was born in Kuala Lumpur, Malaysia on July 5, 1966. She grew up in Venezuela and then San Francisco, California and after high school, studied voice and dance before pursuing acting as a career. She studied at the American Conservatory Theater and has performed soprano roles with the San Francisco Opera.', 'Kuala Lumpur, Malaysia', 1, '/2VOsPvoV2vmEUd1O2KjW3kcN8JD.jpg'),
