        (1223, 'Joel Coen', '1954-11-29', 'American filmmaker Joel David Coen is known for writing, directing and producing films jointly with his brother Ethan Jesse Coen; professionally they are known as the Coen brothers. In 1984, the brothers wrote and directed Blood Simple, their first film together. The film was well received and won awards for Joel''s direction at both the Sundance and Independent Spirit awards.

