Joel has been married to actress Frances McDormand since 1984. They adopted a son from Paraguay, named Pedro McDormand Coen.', 'St Louis Park, Minnesota, USA', 2, '/rgVaJNkZCgMarUcZuUAsVfXMWk3.jpg'),
