Description above from the Wikipedia article Keith Richards, licensed under CC-BY-SA, full list of contributors on Wikipedia.', 'Dartford, Kent, England, United Kingdom', 2, '/t1oa5UsJMmrhNqCIks4jQnAYSQT.jpg'),
