        (2127, 'James Wan', '1977-02-27', 'James Wan is a Malaysian-born Australian producer, screenwriter, and film director of Chinese heritage. He is widely known for directing the horror film Saw and creating Billy the puppet. He also directed Dead Silence, Death Sentence and Insidious.', 'Kuching, Sarawak, Malaysia', 5, '/9AlAMoHVDUX8GVOTw6JOyKil8k9.jpg'),
