        (2744, 'Carmen Maura', '1945-09-15', 'Carmen García Maura (born September 15, 1945) is a Spanish actress. In a career that has spanned six decades, Maura is best known for her collaborations with noted Spanish film director Pedro Almodóvar.', 'Madrid, Spain', 2, '/6YU3CAWmlSy13aRUG2QWRZlJab5.jpg'),
