        (2838, 'Chloë Sevigny', '1974-11-18', 'Chloë Stevens Sevigny (born November 18, 1974) is an American film actress, fashion designer and former model. Sevigny became known for her broad fashion career in the mid-1990s, both for modeling and for her work at New York''s Sassy magazine, which labeled her the new "it girl" at the time, garnering her attention within New York''s fashion scene.

