        (4759, 'David Kellogg', '1952-01-01', 'From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia.

David Kellogg (born 1952) is an American film, commercial, and music video director.

Kellogg has gained prominence for dozens of television spots that he has created for clients such as Pepsi, Fuji, AT&amp;T, Sprite, Coke, Nike, Apple, IBM, MCI, United Airlines, and Mercedes Benz. He is part of Anonymous Content, a commercials and music video production company in Los Angeles, California.

