        (4971, 'Bud Cort', '1948-03-29', 'Bud Cort (born Walter Edward Cox on March 29, 1948) is an American film and stage actor, writer, and director. He is best known for his portrayals of Harold in Hal Ashby''s 1971 film Harold and Maude and the titular hero in Robert Altman''s 1970 film Brewster McCloud. Both films have large cult followings today.', 'New Rochelle, New York, USA', 1, '/kI7N8eeX8TBWBGFQCZWfKZGbrZ6.jpg'),
