        (6907, 'Annie Corley', NULL, 'From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia. Annie Corley is an American actress who has appeared in a wide variety of films and television shows since 1990. Her most notable role to date was playing Meryl Streep''s daughter in the film The Bridges of Madison County.

