He has won a Golden Globe, as well as BAFTA, a César Award, a Golden Palm, two nominations for the Golden Lion and an Academy Award nomination.', 'Brooklyn, New York, USA', 1, '/uTAq7otu6P5ogsJqWAKCzcNTIn9.jpg'),
